description: Retrieves a list of overrides currently specified for an on-call rotation.

parameters.name: RotationId
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the rotation to retrieve information about.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The date and time for the beginning of a time range for listing overrides.

parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The date and time for the end of a time range for listing overrides.

nested_items.name: RotationOverrides
nested_items.description: A list of rotation overrides in the specified time range.

nested_items.name: RotationOverrideId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the override to an on-call rotation.

nested_items.name: NewContactIds
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) of the contacts assigned to the override of the on-call rotation.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The time a rotation override begins.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The time a rotation override ends.

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The time a rotation override was created.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of items to return. Use this token to get the next set of results.
